EC2 Instance

SSH into your EC2 Instance

To SSH into your EC2 Instance

ssh ec2-user@PublicIPAddress
Permission denied will be shown

ssh -i nameofpemfile ec2-user@PublicIPAddress 
chmod 0400 nameofpemfile

SECURITY GROUP -
Security groups acts a firewall to an EC2 Instance
A single SG can be attached to multiple EC2 Instances
They are region/VPN specific.

By default 
    All inbound traffic are blocked.
    All outbound traffic are allowed.
    


